# --- Production session + state storage on Upstash (or Vercel KV) ---
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=https://your-instance.upstash.io
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=your-token
# Or, if Vercel KV is connected:
# KV_REST_API_URL=...
# KV_REST_API_TOKEN=...
#
# Without these the app falls back to an in-process Map (fine for local dev,
# breaks on Vercel because each function invocation gets a fresh process).
